episodes.title: Two Tonys
episodes.plot: Some of the old guards are released from prison and want to get back in the action. Chris and Paulie are at each other's throats over matters of money and respect, and Tony decides to tell Dr. Melfi what's really on his mind.

episodes.title: Rat Pack
episodes.plot: Carmine's passing opens new wounds, while cousin Tony wants to put his past behind him. Tony Soprano, meanwhile, discovers a traitor.

episodes.title: Where's Johnny?
episodes.plot: With Carmine's passing and Feech's arrival, turf wars are breaking out around New Jersey. Junior's mental health, meanwhile, starts to decline.

episodes.title: All Happy Families
episodes.plot: Feech makes a pain of himself by trying to return to his past glory. Carmela tries to work with Anthony's teacher to rein in their out-of-control son.

episodes.title: Irregular Around the Margins
episodes.plot: A car crash puts Tony and Adriana in a compromising position, and Cousin Tony tries to keep Chris from getting the wrong impression and the wrong information.

episodes.title: Sentimental Education
episodes.plot: Carmela has another furtive romance collapse, while Tony B. throws away a chance to turn his life around.

episodes.title: In Camelot
episodes.plot: Tony learns about his father through the man's mistress, while Chris' friend learns that there are habits more harmful to your health than heroin.

episodes.title: Marco Polo
episodes.plot: An uncomfortable party leads Tony and Carmela to a partial reconciliation, while cousin Tony gets an offer he decides not to refuse.

episodes.title: Unidentified Black Males
episodes.plot: Tony finds out that his cousin wants a bigger share of responsibilities, while Finn makes an embarrassing discovery about Vito.

episodes.title: Cold Cuts
episodes.plot: Chris and cousin Tony do some digging to make sure old secrets stay buried, while Janice puts her marriage in jeopardy with her fierce temper.

episodes.title: The Test Dream
episodes.plot: Cousin Tony heads off to avenge the death of his good friend, while a dream reveals to Tony what he must do to prevent a full-scale war.

episodes.title: Long Term Parking
episodes.plot: Tony makes a request to Johnny Sack on behalf of his cousin, and Adriana makes a request to the FBI, followed by one to Chris.

episodes.title: All Due Respect
episodes.plot: Tony realizes that he must take care of family messes himself in order to keep the peace within his own clan.
